{
  "texts": [
    "Experiment and Results Discussion 4.1 Experimental Environment and Parameter Configuration The experiments were conducted using Ubuntu 18.04, an Intel Xeon E5-2637 v4 CPU, 32GB Samsung RAM, and four NVIDIA Titan V GPUs.",
    "The software stack comprised PyTorch 1.10, Python 3.7, CUDA 11.4 and cuDNN 8.2.4.",
    "To ensure effective experiments, batchsize was set to 200 and epochs to 60 during training.",
    "Training proceeded in two phases: cross-entropy and reinforcement learning.",
    "The learning rate was 1e-4 for cross-entropy and 5e-6 for reinforcement learning."
  ]
}